{"tid":2338774,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"亞視受疫情打擊現財困　平安夜公佈全員減薪一成","createTime":"2020-12-24T08:24:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T11:55:16.000Z","uid":130626,"like":6,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"45a5346d155bb7a3bd980cb08a4304d5f3143c10","tid":2338774,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T08:24:37.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎第四波疫情肆虐，港人今年迎來「不一樣」的聖誕節，不少苦撐經營的公司更迎來難言快樂的聖誕節。今日（２４日）平安夜，亞洲電視數碼媒體董事鄧俊杰向員工發出通知，「因公司業務受到疫情打擊令財務出現少許困難」，各員工由明年一月一日起減薪一成，「盼各位能繼續堅守崗位為未來日子打拚」。<br />\n<br />\n記者向亞洲電視數碼媒體查詢，暫未獲回覆。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201224/418787984603615232460319.png/yAQoOJYmDy-NzSWtzs_8WJtrYNLqN3q2ExNJYBMTSWA?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201224%2F418787984603615232460319.png%2FyAQoOJYmDy-NzSWtzs_8WJtrYNLqN3q2ExNJYBMTSWA%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=498a969f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76060e3beb34bd5e8ccb9a41a4f043e2f80b710b","tid":2338774,"uid":331590,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T08:26:49.000Z","msg":"點解仲未汁"},{"pid":"0956e96eba1f83e5134f6e8bf0b615fe8d9d800a","tid":2338774,"uid":48276,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T08:26:57.000Z","msg":"江魚仲係唔係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/catxm/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef4edd686befcb890e0178e214127c357c787293","tid":2338774,"uid":34409,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T08:27:15.000Z","msg":"原來仲出到人工架？"},{"pid":"88ea4f6dcb7f638061a4d7aa2f58951da1dff742","tid":2338774,"uid":289214,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T08:29:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K2kXVMe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK2kXVMe.png&h=d9e66059&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"82a92e5d3005d55ee44c2db817a0dc76705cdd4b","tid":2338774,"uid":2054,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"76060e3beb34bd5e8ccb9a41a4f